def generate_fibonacci_up_to_n(N: int) -> list[int]:
    series = [0]
    prev_num = 1
    curr_num = 1
    while curr_num <= N:
        series.append(curr_num)
        next_num = prev_num + curr_num
        prev_num = curr_num
        curr_num = next_num
    return series
